name: LEGO MINDSTORMS EV3 Project
summary: An EV3 file is a project created by LEGO MINDSTORMS EV3, an app for commanding LEGO MINDSTORMS EV3 robots. It contains all of the project assets, including .EV3P programs, .EV3E experiments, .RGF graphics, .RSF sounds, building instructions, and My Block commands.
